The paper focuses on image manipulation detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). It also involves steganalysis, which is a subfield of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper deals with detecting tampering artifacts, which is related to computer security (cs.CR). The paper proposes a two-stream network and trains it end-to-end, which involves machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper deals with feature extraction and fusion, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
